    "en": {
      "title": "The Nugegoda Police have done a job in this month's pay slip",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to police sources, the police officers of Nugegoda Police Division have been in a lot of trouble due to the fact that some of them have received less salary and others have not received any salary.",
        "This was revealed yesterday (25) after an inspection was conducted after the salaries were banked for those officials.",
        "The sources state that most of the paid people have received the salary they received in January 2021 and the police officers who came for duty in Nugegoda Police Division from February till now have not received any salary in the bank.",
        "Thousands of officers as well as special officers from 17 police stations belonging to Nugegoda Police Superintendent's jurisdiction, namely Mirihana, Maharagama, Kaduwela, Homagama, Hanwella, Meegoda, Wellampitiya, Athurigiriya, Malambe, Boralasgamuwa, Navagamuwa, Thalangama, Mulleriya, Malabe, Kottawa, Welikada, and Padukka. The officers working in the departments were also in a lot of trouble due to this.",
        "In the meantime, some police officers who have been suspended have also received their salaries from other sources.",
        "Police Media Spokesperson Senior Superintendent of Police Advocate Mr. Nihal Talduwa said that he would look into this matter and give an answer. But tried to connect to the phone on several occasions but could not"
      ],
